msgid "SEIR"
msgstr "叙利亚"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR.rst:4
#: 8b23c474a6bb42e8b3204986b0620a26
msgid ""
"The SEIR Model [1]_ assumes that infection spreads only through links "
"between neighboring nodes in a graph :math:`G=(V,E)`. Each node is in one of"
" four states: :math:`S` (susceptible), :math:`E` (exposed/incubating), "
":math:`I` (infected), or :math:`R` (recovered). A susceptible node :math:`i`"
" becomes exposed by its infected neighbors :math:`j \\in N(i)` with rate "
":math:`\\beta`, exposed nodes become infectious with rate :math:`\\alpha`, "
"and infected nodes recover with rate :math:`\\gamma`:"
msgstr ""
"SEIR模型[1] 假设感染只通过相邻的节点之间的联系在图:math:`G=(V,E)'中传播. 每个节点分为四个州之一: \" S \" (可接受)、"
" \" E \" (暴露/孵化)、 \" I \" (感染)、 \" R \" (恢复)。 一个易受感染的节点:math:`i ' "
"被感染的邻居暴露出来。math:`j\\in N(i)',比例:math:``\\beta', 暴露的节点会感染,比例:math:`alpha', "
"并且感染的节点会恢复。"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR.rst:9
#: 8f77f806971f436cb0be5681aa2c72e3
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"\\frac{dS_i}{dt} &= -\\beta \\sum_{j\\in N(i)} S_i I_j, \\\\\n"
"\\frac{dE_i}{dt} &= \\beta \\sum_{j\\in N(i)} S_i I_j - \\alpha E_i, \\\\\n"
"\\frac{dI_i}{dt} &= \\alpha E_i - \\gamma I_i, \\\\\n"
"\\frac{dR_i}{dt} &= \\gamma I_i .\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""
"开始{对齐}\n"
"\\ frac{ dS i}{dt}\\\\\\\\\\ beta\\ sum\\j\\ in N(i)}S i I j,\\\\\\\\\n"
"\\ frac{ dE i}{dt}\\\\ beta\\ sum {j\\ in N(i)} S i I j -\\ alpha E i,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n"
"\\ frac{ dI i}{dt}\\\\ alpha E i -\\gamma I i,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n"
"\\ frac{ dR i}{dt}\\\\\\gamma I i 。\n"
"结束{对齐}"

