#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR.rst:71
#: 0bb430658a584802a904219b2aa97a90
msgid ""
"Node states are represented by three Boolean indicator vectors :math:`h, e, "
"r \\in \\{0,1\\}^N`, where :math:`h_i=1` denotes ``infected`` or "
"``exposed``, :math:`h_i=0` denotes ``recovered`` or ``susceptible``, and "
":math:`(h_i,e_i,r_i)=(1,0,0)` denotes ``infected``, "
":math:`(h_i,e_i,r_i)=(1,1,0)` denotes ``exposed``, "
":math:`(h_i,e_i,r_i)=(0,0,1)` denotes ``recovered``, "
":math:`(h_i,e_i,r_i)=(0,0,0)` denotes ``susceptible``. The update of the "
"system at step :math:`k` is decomposed into three stages:"
msgstr ""
"节点状态由三个布尔指标矢量表示:`h, e, r \\ in \\{0, 1 \\}^n',其中:`h "
"i=1'表示\"感染\"或\"暴露\",`math:`h i=0'表示\"恢复\"或\"可接受\",`math:`(h i,e i,r "
"i)=(1,0)'表示\"感染\",`(h i,e i,r i)=(1,1,0)表示\"感染\",`(1,0)表示\"暴露\",`(h i,e i,r "
"i)=(0,0)表示\",`恢复\",`(h i,e i,r i)=(0,0)表示\". 系统分三个阶段更新:"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR.rst:77
#: 4cd2fb8dafe0431486764a2a5b60153d
msgid ""
"Each infected neighbor :math:`j` of node :math:`i` transmits a log-"
"probability contribution for exposure (S→E)"
msgstr "每个受感染的邻居:math:`j' 节点:math:`i ' 传递接触的日志概率(S E)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR.rst:79
#: f98edbee55b84f79a03df3750b8bfabb
msgid ""
"m_{ji}^{(k)} = \\mathbf{1}\\!\\left(h_j^{(k-1)}=1 \\land "
"e_j^{(k-1)}=0\\right)\\,\\log(1-\\beta)"
msgstr "m {ji}^{(k)}=\\ mathbf{1}\\!}\\左(h j^{(k-1)}\\land e j^{(k-1)\\0\\右)\\,\\log(1-\\β)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR.rst:85
#: c37e5c19b880455b912b74b7b39d572e
msgid ""
"Node :math:`i` collects contributions from all neighbors :math:`N(i)` to "
"compute its exposure probability"
msgstr "节点 : math:`i'收集所有邻居的贡献 : math:`N(i)'计算其暴露概率"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR.rst:87
#: a71422a61d2e43548a4e05396c9a4338
msgid "m_i^{(k)} = 1 - \\exp\\!\\left( \\sum_{j \\in N(i)} m_{ji}^{(k)} \\right)"
msgstr "m i^{(k)}=1 -\\exp\\!\\左(\\sum {j\\in N(i)} m {ji}^{(k)}\\右)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR.rst:92
#: 766cd81b0e1440508789f1374fab1035
msgid ""
"The indicator variables are updated with independent uniform random "
"variables :math:`U_i^{\\mathrm{exp}}, U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}}, "
"U_i^{\\mathrm{rec}} \\sim \\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)`"
msgstr ""
"指标变量以独立的统一随机变量更新 : math : `U i^{\\ mathrm{exp}}, U i^{\\ mathrm{inf}}, U "
"i^{\\ mathrm{rec}}\\sim\\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)' 。"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SEIR.rst:94
#: 407f3b74d803494ebef0fcb475056441
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
" h_i^{(k)} &=\n"
"\\begin{cases}\n"
"    1, & \\text{if } (U_i^{\\mathrm{exp}} < m_i^{(k)}) \\land (h_i^{(k-1)}=0 \\land r_i^{(k-1)}=0), \\\\[4pt]\n"
"    0, & \\text{if } (U_i^{\\mathrm{rec}} < \\gamma) \\land (h_i^{(k-1)}=1 \\land e_i^{(k-1)}=0), \\\\[4pt]\n"
"    h_i^{(k-1)}, & \\text{otherwise},\n"
"\\end{cases} \\\\[6pt]\n"
"e_i^{(k)} &=\n"
"\\begin{cases}\n"
"    1, & \\text{if } (U_i^{\\mathrm{exp}} < m_i^{(k)}) \\land (h_i^{(k-1)}=0 \\land r_i^{(k-1)}=0), \\\\[4pt]\n"
"    0, & \\text{if } (U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}} < \\alpha) \\land e_i^{(k-1)}=1 , \\\\[4pt]\n"
"    e_i^{(k-1)}, & \\text{otherwise},\n"
"\\end{cases} \\\\[6pt]\n"
"r_i^{(k)} &=\n"
"\\begin{cases}\n"
"    1, & \\text{if } (U_i^{\\mathrm{rec}} < \\gamma) \\land (h_i^{(k-1)}=1 \\land e_i^{(k-1)}=0), \\\\[4pt]\n"
"    r_i^{(k-1)}, & \\text{otherwise}.\n"
"\\end{cases}\n"
"\\end{aligned}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"开始{对齐}\n"
"h(k)}\n"
"开始{ cases}\n"
"1, &\\ text{if} (U i^{\\ mathrm{exp}} < m i^{(k)})\\ land (h i^{(k-1)}\\\\ r i^{(k-1)}\\\\ [4pt]\n"
"0, &\\text{if} (U i^{\\ mathrm{rec}} <\\gamma)\\land(h i^{(k-1)\\1)\\land e i^{(k-1)}\\\\[4pt]\n"
"h i^{(k-1)}, &\\ text{另类},\n"
"\\ end{ cases}\\\\\\ [6pt]\n"
"e i^{(k) }\n"
"开始{ cases}\n"
"1, &\\ text{if} (U i^{\\ mathrm{exp}} < m i^{(k)})\\ land (h i^{(k-1)}\\\\ r i^{(k-1)}\\\\ [4pt]\n"
"0, &\\ text{if} (U i^{\\ mathrm{inf}}} <\\alpha)\\land e (k-1)}=1,\\\\[4pt]\n"
"e i  (k-1)}, &\\ text{另类},\n"
"\\ end{ cases}\\\\\\ [6pt]\n"
"r i^{(k)}\n"
"开始{ cases}\n"
"1, &\\ text{if} (U i^{\\ mathrm{rec}} <\\gamma)\\land (h i^{(k-1)\\1)\\land e i^{(k-1)}\\\\[4pt]\n"
"r i^{(k-1)}, &\\ text{另类}.\n"
"结束{ cases}\n"
"结束{对齐}"

